flowchart TD
  A[Engineer prepares production release] --> B[npm run auth:config:check]
  B -->|missing OIDC or JWKS config| C[Fail before deployable build]
  B -->|production fallback enabled| C
  B -->|valid| D[Write non-secret auth diagnostics artifact]
  D --> E[npm run build]
  E --> F[npm run auth:config:check:vercel]
  F -->|missing env names| G[Block release and notify production config owner]
  F -->|names present| H[Trigger new production deployment]
  H --> I[Inspect Ready deployment, commit, timestamp]
  I --> J[Verify /auth/callback redirect URI in IdP allowlist]
  J --> K[Operator runs production OIDC smoke]
  K --> L[Protected view loads data or intentional empty state]
  L --> M[Auth availability alerts monitor login path and callback failures]
  M --> N[Issue remains production-remediation-pending until evidence is attached]
  C --> O[/sign-in shows no-login-path configuration state]
